<plot>The story of two South Africans who took part in the struggle against Apartheid. It is the story of lives spent in camouflage, in danger and in loneliness but inspired by the vision of a free society. Lives of courage and humanity, but fraught, too, with doubt and disappointment as the contradictions of the armed struggle unfold around them and the ideals which maintain them threaten to fall apart.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?365322</url></doc>
